<D>__{yes.}
<C>__{athos}
<D>__{tell me.}
<C>__{milady}
<D>__{will you spare my life?}
<C>__{athos}
<D>__{i can't.}
<C>__{milady}
<P>__{(remembering another time, another place)}
<D>__{society demands swift justice.}
<P>__{(off his look)}
<D>__{i will take the secret to my grave.}
<C>__{athos}
<D>__{sabine. you'll die for your crimes. nothing can stop that. but how you leave this world is up to you.}
<A>__{milady offers a half smile, takes his hand in hers.}
<C>__{milady}
<D>__{what did the world ever do for me?}
<A>__{hold on athos. milady's hand in his. all that he is feeling.}
